## 2. Your installed tier

**Installed tier: {{ROSTER_TIER}}**

Tiers are additive — STANDARD is MIN-VIABLE plus more seats, FULL is STANDARD plus more seats.
Nothing is ever removed going up a tier, and P7 upgrade mode (§6) is how you move to a higher one
later without losing anything you've already earned.

